FBIS4-62302 "drsov094_i_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-094 Daily Report 16 May 1994 CENTRAL ASIA Kazakhstan Industrial Enterprises Enduring Financial Difficulties Industrial Enterprises Enduring Financial Difficulties LD1605102494 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Kazakh 0800 GMT 16 May 94 LD1605102494 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network Kazakh BFN [Summary] Enterprises in Pavlodar oblast are running into financial difficulties. This year in January, February, and March, 11 percent of enterprises have been at a standstill; 44 percent had to reduce the assets' part of their balances, and 10 percent have not received any profit at all. Settlement of payments between the enterprises is next to impossible.
